Notes: SP's Neuenfeldt hit three pointers for leads of 32-23 and 37-25 in second
half...SP led 43-33 with 8:52 left and went on 12-2 run over next three
minutes...Largest lead in final 15 minutes of first half was three points...
SP had nine of its 13 blocks in first half...SP's Kranz scores career high.
Game.Officials: Daron Lindeman,  Tom Kissinger,  John Furrer
